# AccessTO — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in real values there. .env.local is
# gitignored and must never be committed. Do not put secrets in variables
# prefixed NEXT_PUBLIC_ — those are inlined into the client bundle and are
# not private (see NFR-SEC-1 in the SRS).

# --- Google Maps (required starting Phase 6) ---
# Client-visible by design; secured via HTTP referrer + API restriction on
# the key itself, not by keeping it out of the bundle.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAP_ID=

# --- City of Toronto CKAN API ---
# No API key required for reads. Base URL is fixed in lib/ckanClient.ts
# (https://ckan0.cf.opendata.inter.prod-toronto.ca/api/3/action); no env var
# needed unless you want to override it for local testing.
# CKAN_API_BASE_URL=
